        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JJW for his paper on apterous insects [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">5939</hi>], which contained much new information.</p> 
            <p>Asks JJW for any information he may have on sexual selection.</p>
            <p>Describes an experiment, still untried, of staining tail-feathers of male pigeons in bright colours to find the effect on courtship.</p>
        </abstract>
